#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.107"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.107:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.107:0.2"
msgid "11. Tikavagga "
msgstr "11. Triads "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.107:0.3"
msgid "107. Rāgasutta "
msgstr "107. Greed "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.446, sc1
msgctxt "an6.107:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three things. "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.3"
msgid "Rāgo, doso, moho. "
msgstr "Greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā. "
msgstr "These are the three things. "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "To give up these three things you should develop three things. "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.6"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.7"
msgid "Rāgassa pahānāya asubhā bhāvetabbā, dosassa pahānāya mettā bhāvetabbā, mohassa pahānāya paññā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "You should develop the perception of ugliness to give up greed, love to give up hate, and wisdom to give up delusion. "

msgctxt "an6.107:1.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three things you should develop to give up those three things.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.107:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
